Spatial distribution of the Vegetation transects for the Colonization Pattern experiment (Q. pyrenaica)

Robledal de San Juan (northwestern of Sierra Nevada)

Robledal de Car (southern Sierra Nevada)

Info

This repo contains a visualization of the spatial distribution of the vegetation transects carried out within MIGRAME project (Global Change, Altitudinal Range Shift and Colonization of Degraded Habitats in Mediterranean Mountains). All vegetation data and more info could be accessed in Prez-Luque et al.2015.

This repository is licensed as Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 (CC BY 4.0). You can find more info here. Anyone can use the content of the repository citing as following:

  • Prez-Luque AJ (2020). Spatial visualization of vegetation transects for analyze the colonization pattern of abandonment croplands within Quercus pyrenaica woodlands of Sierra Nevada. .
